text: Uha dakhila karada hai rata nu dina vica ate dina nu rata vica ate usa ne suraja ate cana nu vasa kara dita hai. Hara ika, ika niradharita samem la'i calada hai. Iha alaha hi tuhada raba hai use la'i (sasara di) badasahi hai ate usa tom binham tusim jinham nu pukarade ho uha khazura di gitaka de ika chilake de vi malaka nahim
